flowchart TD
    classDef trigger fill:#eaf3ff,stroke:#5b9bd5,color:#1f2937,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef check fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#f9a825,color:#1f2937,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef pass fill:#eef7ee,stroke:#6aa84f,color:#1f2937,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef fail fill:#fce8e6,stroke:#e53935,color:#b71c1c,stroke-width:1.5px;

    Action[Requested Action\nTransfer / Issue / Redeem]:::trigger
    Action --> Identity[Identity Check\nDID + KYC status]:::check
    Identity --> Whitelist[Whitelist Check\ncounterparty allowed]:::check
    Whitelist --> Policy[Policy Engine\ntransaction rules]:::check
    Policy --> Limits[Limit Check\nholding & velocity caps]:::check
    Limits --> Approved[Approved\naction executes on-chain]:::pass
    Limits --> Rejected[Rejected\nreason logged + notified]:::fail
